reviews.text: Nice spot for vegan lunch - tastes like homemade food and prices are reasonable. Love the spinach noodles with tempeh & sesame sauce and the tomato soup noodles with beancurd rolls.

My sister took me here, since I was looking for something to eat. Original Taste has a few (around 4-5) vegetarian/vegan dishes to choose from, which is very nice! It comes with a cold drink, but you can change it to a warm soup (there are 2 different kinds of veg soups to choose from) for 5HKD extra! I think this little restaurant is cash-only, but it's very affordable! A dish including drink is around 59HKD to 63HKD. +5HKD for soup instead! We were so full! It was very tasty! All in all, it was a very good experience! Thanks sis for taking me here!
Very good food and great fast service.  I ordered the chicken with pineapple with onion sauce and rice and a side of fried vegetarian tofu rolls. The food tastes fresh and lots of flavor.

自家製既食物有水準！
份量夠，少鹽少糖無味精，味道清淡感覺比較健康。
自家制 新鮮蕃茄、菠菜、黑藜麥麵，在其他地方未見過！大部份食物都是自家制的！新鮮！好味！
